PrecisReappointment of MONA BEAUCHEMIN of Verdun, Quebec, and RICHARD QUIRION of Anjou, Quebec, to be full-time members of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montréal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years, effective July 28, 2004.
